  "text": "We show the spacetime coordinate invariances of the T-theory Hamiltonian and Lagrangian requiring new conditions. The transformation of the spacetime background vielbein under → ′ = − was already given as the new Lie derivative in the Hamiltonian formalism [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] :",
